UPDATE: NORWAY TEEN ACQUITTED IN CRACKING CASE
(Source: IDG.net) 
In a widely watched case, a Norway court acquits Jon Lech Johansen of charges related to a program that can be used to crack digital copy-protection on DVDs.
http://www.idg.net/go.cgi?id=779355


